  "texts": [
    "4 Supplementary Evidence",
    "To complement the difference-in-differences analysis of labor market impacts, we simply asked respondents directly: \"Have AI chatbots affected your labor earnings?\"",
    "If so, we followed up with, \"By how much?\"",
    "If AI chatbots were meaningfully changing labor market conditions in exposed occupations, we might expect \"front-line workers\" in those occupations to notice and report such changes.",
    "Appendix E.3 reports workers' perceived earnings impacts from AI chatbots."
  ],
